1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:01,560
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,080
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

3
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:18,440
I just ran into this guy,

4
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,240
and he's so damn cute.

5
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:21,400
His name is Qin.

6
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:22,280
He's from the College of Music.

7
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:24,440
If you rush in now, you're screwed.

8
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:26,200
You gotta do your homework
on him first.

9
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:27,360
Help me.

10
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:28,480
Someone's following me.

11
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,160
The fortune teller was right.

12
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:32,000
She said Qin would ask me for help.

13
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,880
I'm sure
the rest of the results are right, too.

14
00:00:33,970 --> 00:00:35,370
Friends gotta have each other's backs.

15
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:38,720
I've got a plan
for your confession, buddy.

16
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:39,600
Hey!

17
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:41,160
I'm going to win your heart.

18
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:42,640
I'm not asking for your permission.

19
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:43,760
I just want to let you know.

20
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:45,520
I feel like I've been enchanted

21
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:47,160
all because of your voice.

22
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,560
Good luck with that, then.

23
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:50,600
Yay!

24
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,360
- Hey!
- Hey!

25
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,240
You're nothing but snacks.

26
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,880
I'll enjoy crushing you to bits!

27
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:59,560
- Hey! Stop bothering me!
- You freaking snacks!

28
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,600
- Pae!
- Stop it.

29
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,200
- Come and help me already!
- I'm in the team fight!

30
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,560
Don't gang up on me.

31
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:08,680
Gosh!

32
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,960
I died. Damn it!

33
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,320
I'm nothing but a ghost.

34
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,120
Enjoy chasing me, huh?

35
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,560
Hope you like my ult.

36
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,960
How did you know
they were chasing you?

37
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,200
They've been doing that so often.

38
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,760
- Man!
- Come on!

39
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,080
It's over.

40
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,240
Our base got blown to pieces.

41
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,720
- You suck.
- It's because of you.

42
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:34,090
I've got it!

43
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,080
These are
[How to Win Qin's Heart by Duang, the Lover Boy]

44
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,520
my plans to make Qin mine.

45
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:49,830
My Plan A is to treat him to snacks.

46
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:51,200
Here's the latest piece of info I got.

47
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,920
Qin loves eating snacks.

48
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,880
How did you know?

49
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,200
Back at the festival,

50
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,920
he had a ton of snacks.

51
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,120
What's next?

52
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,920
I'm going to win him over
by giving him snacks.

53
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:03,120
If he likes the snacks I gave him,
that means he likes me.

54
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:04,600
How many are you going to give him?

55
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,440
As many as I can afford.

56
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:09,080
Oh, you're going all in?

57
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,720
What if you fail?

58
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,800
I'll go to Plan B, of course!
[Plan B! "Scare him into loving me"]

59
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,360
Scare him into loving me.

60
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,840
I'm going to spook Qin with a ghost.

61
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:20,040
Once he's scared, I'll comfort him.

62
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,880
This way, he's going to fall for me.

63
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,600
That's weird.

64
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,720
Yeah.

65
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:29,760
How do you know
he's scared of this kind of ghost?

66
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,320
Before executing the plan,
dress up as believably as you can.

67
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,920
This way,
I can do my part when he's scared.

68
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,880
Oh, hell no!

69
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,520
What would you do
if I got decked in the face?

70
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,280
- Huh?
- Dress up as the ghost yourself!

71
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,640
Who's going to help me with that?

72
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,880
How am I supposed
to comfort him?

73
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,040
Jamie, are you going to...

74
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,079
Hey, stop it.

75
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,130
You have to do something

76
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:53,000
he will remember
for the rest of his life.

77
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,280
Win him over by dressing up as a ghost.

78
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,840
It's such a unique take.

79
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:01,800
It's as unique as your stupidity.

80
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,400
Hey, but this one's not stupid.

81
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,240
I'm sold.

82
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,560
I want him to remember every moment
I try to hit on him.

83
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,320
I'm blushing.

84
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,520
You two are out of your minds.

85
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,680
I don't think it's going to work.

86
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:13,800
I don't think
Qin will recognize you in disguise.

87
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,440
You're going to scare him
for a lifetime.

88
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,240
Then we'll go with Plan C.

89
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,040
Bug him at every moment.
[Plan C! "Bug him at every moment"]

90
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:25,079
I'm going to be around him
at every given moment.

91
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,320
What if he punches you in the face?

92
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,840
I have to make sure this is safe,

93
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:34,800
so he doesn't clobber me
when he sees me.

94
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,240
I acknowledge your determination.

95
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:40,360
Even though
all of your plans are stupid...

96
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,400
I'll help.

97
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,200
Me, too. You can count on me.

98
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:48,320
I want to witness
your stupidity up close.

99
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,920
You're so unique, you know?

100
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,760
You are. Do you get it?

101
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,800
See? This is why we're friends.

102
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,200
- Right.
- Yeah.

103
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:24,960
♫I'm not leaving soon, so bear with me♫

104
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:30,100
♫Wherever you are
is where I'll always be♫

105
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:34,000
♫Wherever you go,
I'll find you eventually♫

106
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,320
♫You may push me away, but I won't flee♫

107
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:39,360
♫Who would you love if it weren't me?♫

108
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,640
♫So, wanna make a deal, maybe?♫

109
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:44,040
♫Alright, alright, don't worry♫

110
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:46,320
♫Just date me first, take it easy♫

111
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,720
♫I'll be so cute you'll fall naturally♫

112
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,040
♫No matter what,
you'll always run into me♫

113
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,440
♫Okay, okay, let it be♫

114
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,760
♫I know you're also into me,♫

115
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,280
♫Don't you feel the same? I can see♫

116
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:04,560
♫I'll keep on flirting,
don't try to avoid me♫

117
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:09,360
♫'Cause I won't stop
till you fall for me♫

118
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:13,920
♫I'll keep on flirting,
I won't stop, I guarantee♫

119
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:20,360
♫I'll love you hard,
and once you say yes, I'll set you free♫

120
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,480
Oh, what should I get?

121
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,880
How about this one?

122
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:40,159
That's not a snack! Damn it!

123
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,120
How many of these should I get?

124
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,520
As many as you can.

125
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,920
Gosh, you're the real lover boy.

126
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,760
I'm definitely going to win his heart.

127
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,320
Write him some notes, too.

128
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,120
Sure!

129
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:06,640
Done! Let's go!

130
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,760
We're done!

131
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,560
Go, go, go!

132
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,040
Qin is on his way to his class now!

133
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,080
Pae, help us attach the notes!

134
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,530
He'll be too full to read the notes.

135
00:06:13,570 --> 00:06:16,040
- Help me with the notes!
- I'm working on them!

136
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,040
Arrange them properly, please!

137
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,520
- Stop fighting!
- Put that at the bottom!

138
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:21,680
Why are you attaching
two notes for this box?

139
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,320
- Just fix it, then!
- The ice cream...

140
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,160
Hurry up!

141
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:25,360
What about this one?

142
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,360
- This one?
- Shove it in the bag!

143
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,480
Go, go, go!

144
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,000
I'm going now!

145
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,000
I'm the one giving him the snacks, no?

146
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,640
Hey!

147
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,320
Oh, hey!

148
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,560
Hey, that's Qin.

149
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,920
Come on.

150
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,640
Not interested in
your so-called lover boy?

151
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,960
My lover boy? No.

152
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:06,480
If he's not yours, then whose is he?

153
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,400
My assignment comes first.

154
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,120
I'll deal with other stuff later.

155
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,280
Oh, I feel so sorry for him.

156
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,760
Qin!

157
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,040
I got you snacks.

158
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,800
Wait up.

159
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,320
At least talk to him for a minute.

160
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,760
What do you want me to say?

161
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,560
What brings you here, Duang?

162
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,520
What type of answer did you expect?

163
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,240
Enough.

164
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,520
I'd say it's the wind of love.

165
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,800
If you guys want to talk, go ahead.

166
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,120
I need to submit my assignment.

167
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,000
It's too hot out here.

168
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:44,920
Qin.

169
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:48,240
Will you accept snacks from me?

170
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,440
These are your favorites.

171
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,480
How did you know that they are?

172
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:57,000
I saw you bought a ton of these
back at the Loy Krathong Festival.

173
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,080
Don't want them.

174
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,160
I'll see you again!

175
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,640
It's too early for me to give up.

176
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,080
Prepare to be mine!

177
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:26,080
The wind of love
will find its way back to you.

178
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,960
Not it.

179
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,080
Or maybe Krahang?

180
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,240
What about Ramphueng?

181
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,960
No, Master would exorcise me.

182
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,880
What about a zombie?

183
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,880
Are you alright?

184
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,120
Care to see a doctor?

185
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:21,920
What?

186
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,440
When are you going to help me?

187
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,440
I need to spook him tomorrow.

188
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,360
I'm still not in the mood.

189
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,920
Go eat that somewhere else
if you're no help.

190
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,960
What? Just tell me what you need.

191
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:34,360
What ghost should I dress up as?

192
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,560
You really want to do it, don't you?

193
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,240
I'll help.

194
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,440
Any ideas?

195
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,400
A delusional ghost?

196
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,040
I'm going to smack you in the face.

197
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,920
How about a kuman thong?

198
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,800
Qin will address you nicely.

199
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,000
It's perfect.

200
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,320
Brother Duang,
can you offer me red soda?

201
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,680
Brother, my ass!

202
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,720
Be serious.

203
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,000
How about a vampire?

204
00:09:59,000 --> 00:09:59,840
Pretty cool, huh?

205
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,400
It is cool,

206
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,560
but is it going to suit me?

207
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,600
You don't want any of my ideas.

208
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,120
Can you make up your mind?

209
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:12,560
I want a ghost that's scary but cute.

210
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,960
Then there's only one option left.

211
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,160
Chucky.

212
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,240
Chucky.

213
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,720
Hey.

214
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,940
Chucky.

215
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:35,160
Hey, stop it!

216
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,400
That's hilarious.

217
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,600
- Oh, shit!
- Shit!

218
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,520
You scared me.

219
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:53,400
You nailed the costume.

220
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,440
Of course. I have to.

221
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,480
I'm not studying this for nothing.

222
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,560
Damn, this is cool.

223
00:10:57,600 --> 00:11:01,360
How are you going to confess your love
while wearing the costume?

224
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:04,920
I've got it all planned. Just you wait.

225
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:08,240
What's the plan?
Do we have to do anything?

226
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:09,960
You do. Now, listen.

227
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,720
Jamie, go and follow Qin.

228
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:15,000
I think he's going to take
his usual exit.

229
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:17,080
I'm going to jump scare him
in front of this building.

230
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,070
Do tell me if something's up.

231
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:20,380
Pae, stay with me and scout ahead.

232
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,090
- Let's go.
- Okay.

233
00:11:22,130 --> 00:11:23,080
Let's do a group chant.

234
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,880
Hey!

235
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:24,790
Come on!

236
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:25,920
Damn you!

237
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:26,960
Just get on with it.

238
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,000
Come on, let's get going.

239
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,880
I have to go now. I'm busy.

240
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,300
Yeah, I have to go as well.

241
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,560
Bye, Qin.

242
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,640
See you.

243
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:51,840
[Qin is all alone now]

244
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,440
Shit.

245
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,240
What do I do?

246
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,480
Hey!

247
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,880
Why did you get scared?

248
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,160
I'm the one who's supposed to be scared.

249
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,280
- Hey!
- What?

250
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:19,840
It's not going according to plan.

251
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,080
Qin is coming this way.

252
00:12:21,370 --> 00:12:22,360
Get ready.

253
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,840
Get ready?

254
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,680
Do I still look cute?

255
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,560
No.

256
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:27,840
Enough. Duang, you can't do this.

257
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,160
No, you can.

258
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,040
Go.

259
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,200
Wait, Duang!

260
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:32,960
Your knives.

261
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,960
Shit! These look too realistic!

262
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,000
Go.

263
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,680
Ow!

264
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,200
Hey, it's me, Duang.

265
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:08,200
It's you!
Stop fucking clowning around!

266
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,120
- Ah!
- Hey!

267
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,160
Shit...

268
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,960
I should abandon the plan.

269
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,000
If I scare him,

270
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,630
I'll probably get decked in the face.

271
00:14:16,890 --> 00:14:17,640
