Just earlier.

379
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,160
Right,

380
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:16,000
so you were late
because you talked to that guy?

381
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:21,080
So, how did it go?
With how he's pursuing you,

382
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:23,520
