No.

384
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:39,800
You think something's off with him?

385
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:42,040
I do.

386
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:46,600
I think that this lover boy
might just have a chance.

387
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,760
