418
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:34,560
Liking Qin, of course.

419
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:39,760
I'm second to none.

420
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:41,560
What?

421
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,360
It's nothing but the truth.

422
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:46,800
Yes, I know that, sweetie.

423
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:49,720
So what next?

424
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:52,040
I don't even know
how to pursue Qin anymore.

425
00:23:54,800 --> 00:23:57,000
Even though
I really like him, it's like...

426
00:23:57,880 --> 00:23:58,960
Do you feel me?

427
00:23:59,000 --> 00:23:59,880
I don't.

428
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:00,880
Me neither.

429
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:03,960
I do understand

430
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,880
