469
00:26:09,620 --> 00:26:11,040
Follow what your heart says.

470
00:26:11,080 --> 00:26:13,960
But there's only a thin line
between pursuing and stalking.

471
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,920
You've gotta be genuine.

472
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:20,340
If he gets uncomfortable
with the way you're doing it,

473
00:26:20,380 --> 00:26:23,320
then you're a stalker in his eyes.

474
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:29,320
I think being direct
and genuine is the best way to go.

475
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:32,640
For me, that's all it takes.

476
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:37,040
Mm, that's good advice.

477
00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:38,920
If he likes you back,

478
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:42,960
maybe he'll take you
on a first-class flight.

479
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:45,440
Think about it,
if you two really get along,

480
00:26:46,060 --> 00:26:49,720
you might just be the first pup
who gets to fly a plane.

481
00:26:52,080 --> 00:26:53,280
Swear you're not copying me.

482
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,080
What?!

483
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,280
Copying, my butt.

484
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:57,920
It's not even related.

485
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,160
You guys are good at this.

486
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:01,600
Of course, we totally are.

487
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:03,480
Not when it comes to yourself, though.

488
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:04,240
What...

489
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,120
Is that an insult?

490
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:06,000
No, it's a compliment.

491
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:07,040
Alright, then.

492
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:10,120
Coaches don't participate
in the game, you know.

493
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,560
That's because the coach is pathetic.

494
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:14,160
Right?

495
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:16,840
Who is?

496
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,480
I already washed my hands.

497
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,800
Hello,

498
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:31,320
