518
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:46,720
Just kidding.

519
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:47,840
Come on, let me see.

520
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:51,280
What?
That's all you got after all that effort?

521
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,680
Yeah, lots of them
didn't come out great.

522
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:56,240
But my feelings for Qin
are a million times more than this!

523
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:58,800
Don't make that face.

524
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:01,640
You were the ones who told me
to do something Qin likes.

525
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:03,200
I know he loves snacks,

526
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,960
so I made these for him.

527
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:06,520
Right...

528
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,720
Why didn't you
make them into those boxes?

529
00:30:08,760 --> 00:30:09,760
What boxes?

530
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:12,520
Well, blind boxes.

531
00:30:12,560 --> 00:30:13,680
You've never heard of them?

532
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,440
