533
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,520
Two: dark and white chocolates.

534
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:17,720
Hey, that's perfect.

535
00:30:17,840 --> 00:30:20,280
Make them into blind boxes
and give them to Qin.

536
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:21,720
You'll have something
to discuss with him.

537
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:24,120
Wow, that's a brilliant idea.

538
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:27,840
This way, Duang won't be a sad pup
if Qin rejects his gifts.

539
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:29,560
And how do I make them?

540
00:30:38,800 --> 00:30:39,800
Give those back.

541
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:42,560
Why did you take them?

542
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,840
So there won't be any left for us?

543
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:09,880
Yeah, what should we eat?

544
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:12,760
Oh?

545
00:31:16,340 --> 00:31:18,280
Could I have
one or two minutes of your time?

546
00:31:18,520 --> 00:31:19,960
I'd like to ask you for a favor.

547
00:31:20,280 --> 00:31:21,440
Is this a direct sale?

548
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,320
I don't have time.

549
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,880
Here's your Christmas gift.

550
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,560
I made it myself.

551
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,560
I just wanted to give you a gift

552
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:33,280
and play a game with you.

553
00:31:35,080 --> 00:31:36,320
I told you I didn't have time.

554
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:38,720
Okay,

555
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:40,400
let me know when you're free.

556
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,810
I'll wait for you right here.

557
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:46,040
This lover boy is not giving up, huh?

558
00:31:46,080 --> 00:31:46,840
Mm.

559
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,960
Duang, let me tell you something.

560
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:53,320
Approaching his friends
can go a long way.

561
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:56,280
If you have extra,
maybe give those to them.

562
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,920
Sure. Consider it done for next time.

563
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,280
Don't forget my share.

564
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:01,160
Copy.

565
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:05,640
If I agree to play along,
will you leave?

566
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,320
Yes,

567
00:32:08,360 --> 00:32:10,120
I'll leave if you play with me.

568
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,440
You guys go ahead to practice.

569
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:15,760
I'll join you later.

570
00:32:16,520 --> 00:32:17,400
Here.

571
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,840
Are you going to play or what?

572
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:49,720
What do you want me to do?

573
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,200
Okay.

574
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,640
Here, let me explain the rules.

575
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:57,270
If you get dark chocolate,
you can request one thing from me.

576
00:32:57,310 --> 00:33:00,360
But if you get white chocolate,
I can request one thing from you.

577
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:05,600
Go ahead.

578
00:33:22,320 --> 00:33:23,520
Mm, white.

579
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,640
What's your request?

580
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:30,160
I want...

581
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,440
This isn't going to end well, is it?

582
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,280
Can I take you home?

583
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,240
I like walking.

584
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:51,720
That means more time together...

585
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,400
I also like walking.

586
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:58,280
I can even walk to Bangkok.

587
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:04,560
Then you wait.

588
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,400
I have to finish my practice.

589
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:09,920
Yes, I can wait.

590
00:34:47,679 --> 00:34:49,159
Please let me carry your stuff.

591
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:50,639
I can do it myself.

592
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,120
But I want to help.

593
00:34:55,159 --> 00:34:56,159
You can, by leaving it to me.

594
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,000
Right,

595
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,760
you look so cute
when you practice music.

596
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:03,480
I'm happy to be walking by your side.

597
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,720
Can you do so quietly?

598
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:09,960
Of course!

599
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:46,840
I think we should
seek shelter from the rain.

600
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,640
I'll count from one to three,

601
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,080
and we'll run over there.

602
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,640
One,

603
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,480
two, three!

604
00:35:58,040 --> 00:35:58,720
Whoa!

605
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:01,480
Qin, hurry.

606
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,640
Come on, Qin.

607
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:03,640
♫You and me, standing way too close♫

608
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:06,760
♫Feels like everything is moving slow♫

609
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:10,000
♫Something inside
is getting hard to hold♫

610
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:13,160
♫That feeling I gotta keep low♫

611
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:17,440
♫I forgot how long it has been♫

612
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:20,840
♫I lost track of time so much that
I almost forgot to breathe♫

613
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:24,280
♫We still have time
if you're not in a hurry♫

614
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:26,400
♫Please let time slip by♫

615
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:30,120
♫Just take our time
and let it slowly flow♫

616
00:37:30,160 --> 00:37:33,520
♫Stay a little longer,
don't leave me here alone♫

617
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:36,960
♫Just want to be with you,
even if we're stuck in the rain,♫

618
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:40,520
♫I just want to be here
'cause you make me feel at home♫

619
00:37:40,560 --> 00:37:43,880
♫I can feel your heartbeat♫

620
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:47,400
♫Every time you breathe♫

621
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:50,840
♫I don't know if we'll ever
get to have this moment again♫

622
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:54,280
♫So please, don't leave this place♫

623
00:38:59,160 --> 00:39:00,160
Here you go.

624
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:01,120
Satisfied?

625
00:39:03,120 --> 00:39:03,880
Of course.

626
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,120
Leave, then.

627
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:07,920
Hey!

628
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:12,400
Can you follow me back on IG?

629
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:16,960
Weren't you only allowed one request?

630
00:39:19,120 --> 00:39:19,920
Okay,

631
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:21,720
can we play again, then?

632
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,280
No, I won't.

633
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:27,960
Please do!

634
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,840
I have so many chocolates at my place.

635
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:30,960
Are you sure?

636
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,200
We can play multiple rounds, too.

637
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:32,960
No.

638
00:39:34,180 --> 00:39:36,360
You like chocolate, don't you?

639
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:39,040
I have tons I can bring for you.

640
00:39:39,200 --> 00:39:41,000
Please play with me!

641
00:39:46,720 --> 00:39:47,720
Don't push it.

642
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:56,280
New information acquired:

643
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:58,240
this is Qin's condo.

644
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:59,680
My boyfriend's place!

645
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:00,960
My future boyfriend...

646
00:40:11,620 --> 00:40:14,720
If you get dark chocolate,
you can request one thing from me.

647
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:17,560
But if you get white chocolate,
I can request one thing from you.

648
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:30,800
Hey, everyone.

649
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:33,560
Hello, Coach.

650
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:34,600
Hi, hi.

651
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,920
Hey, what about PK?

652
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,240
Huh?

653
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:45,920
I'm here, Coach.

654
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,920
You're late again.

655
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:58,240
Alright, go practice.

656
00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,720
Start with the warm-up.

657
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:21,080
Go, sprint to touch the line.

658
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:51,640
Alright, let's take ten.

659
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:52,440
Go.

660
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:05,760
Right, Qin.

661
00:43:06,040 --> 00:43:07,520
How was yesterday with Duang?

662
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:09,000
Huh?

663
00:43:09,240 --> 00:43:10,720
How come you guys
walked home together?

664
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:11,760
I'm confused.

665
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,240
It was just a walk home.

666
00:43:14,760 --> 00:43:15,960
You took the same route home?

667
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,600
No.

668
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:19,440
So you're opening up to him?

669
00:43:21,120 --> 00:43:21,960
What?

670
00:43:22,400 --> 00:43:23,680
No, it's just...

671
00:43:24,160 --> 00:43:27,160
If you are,
I'll give him your class schedule.

672
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:29,520
He's been asking me for it every day.

673
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:32,680
We'll see.

674
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:35,920
So you're gonna be friends for now?

675
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:37,880
Not friends.

676
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:39,880
I don't allow friends to pursue me.

677
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:41,360
Friends are friends.

678
00:43:42,200 --> 00:43:44,800
If someone doesn't want friendship,
they shouldn't approach me that way.

679
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:48,080
Okay.

680
00:43:48,320 --> 00:43:49,720
That's not suspicious at all.

681
00:43:50,280 --> 00:43:52,080
Qin knows what he wants.

682
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,320
Let's go, guys.

683
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:00,560
Let's practice.

684
00:44:00,600 --> 00:44:02,160
When he said, "We'll see,"

685
00:44:02,200 --> 00:44:04,400
was that a yes
to sending Duang the class schedule?

686
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:06,880
Maybe he wants to do it himself.

687
00:44:07,200 --> 00:44:09,120
Keep your nose out of their business.

688
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:12,640
You're right.

689
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:22,960
This isn't right, Jamie.

690
00:44:23,280 --> 00:44:25,760
Don't you think they're exploiting us?

691
00:44:26,030 --> 00:44:27,160
Why did you stop?

692
00:44:27,200 --> 00:44:28,800
Just keep going. It's heavy!

693
00:44:30,040 --> 00:44:31,640
It's heavy. That's why I stopped.

694
00:44:32,520 --> 00:44:33,520
It's just too heavy.

695
00:44:34,600 --> 00:44:36,200
Hey, Duang!

696
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:41,480
Hey, what is it?

697
00:44:41,520 --> 00:44:42,160
These are heavy.

698
00:44:42,640 --> 00:44:43,640
Hold this.

699
00:44:43,680 --> 00:44:45,120
Guys, sorry for troubling you.

700
00:44:45,240 --> 00:44:46,160
What's gotten into you?

701
00:44:47,240 --> 00:44:48,200
Yeah.

702
00:44:49,440 --> 00:44:50,440
- Come on!
- Are you alright?

703
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:52,440
Pae, stop playing dumb already.

704
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:01,280
The word 'cute'
will be overused at this rate.

705
00:45:09,960 --> 00:45:10,960
- Duang!
- Ah!

706
00:45:12,920 --> 00:45:14,880
My name is Alice.

707
00:45:14,920 --> 00:45:17,880
Our university is having an open house.

708
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:21,920
This means
there will be a ton of visitors.

709
00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:23,520
I'm sorry?

710
00:45:24,160 --> 00:45:24,960
Well...

711
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:29,600
I'd like you to dance for
the opening ceremony of the open house.

712
00:45:30,680 --> 00:45:32,080
I'm afraid I can't do that.

713
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:34,880
Aww, Duang.

714
00:45:34,920 --> 00:45:39,000
I expected to hear
a confirmation from you.

715
00:45:39,040 --> 00:45:41,480
I have no other choice but you, Duang.

716
00:45:41,520 --> 00:45:44,200
I can't sing, you see.

717
00:45:44,240 --> 00:45:46,320
My friends call me a tone-deaf singer.

718
00:45:46,360 --> 00:45:47,280
I can't dance either.

719
00:45:47,320 --> 00:45:48,960
So how am I supposed to help you?

720
00:45:49,440 --> 00:45:50,720
Please, Duang.

721
00:45:50,760 --> 00:45:52,080
I need your help.

722
00:45:52,120 --> 00:45:54,320
I'm out of options.

723
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:57,180
I do have a friend
who is really good-looking.

724
00:45:57,220 --> 00:45:58,680
His name is Jamie, and he can sing.

725
00:45:58,720 --> 00:45:59,720
He's a better option.

726
00:45:59,760 --> 00:46:00,960
He's probably around there.

727
00:46:02,040 --> 00:46:03,520
What? Jamie?

728
00:46:03,560 --> 00:46:04,600
I know him well.

729
00:46:04,640 --> 00:46:06,760
He always goes wherever he pleases.

730
00:46:06,800 --> 00:46:08,280
Nobody can put him on the right track.

731
00:46:08,320 --> 00:46:11,480
There's only you left,
my adorable little Duang.

732
00:46:12,640 --> 00:46:13,720
I'm not adorable.

733
00:46:13,760 --> 00:46:14,640
I'm handsome.

734
00:46:18,040 --> 00:46:19,160
Yeah, you're right!

735
00:46:19,200 --> 00:46:20,520
You're extremely handsome.

736
00:46:20,560 --> 00:46:22,680
You're the most handsome guy there is.

737
00:46:22,720 --> 00:46:23,840
Since I was born,

738
00:46:23,880 --> 00:46:27,560
I've never met
someone just as perfect as you.

739
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:30,840
Trust my words.

740
00:46:30,880 --> 00:46:32,600
I never fail.

741
00:46:32,920 --> 00:46:36,160
Anyway, please get back to me.

742
00:46:36,200 --> 00:46:37,880
Don't take too long, okay?
You'll stress me out.

743
00:46:38,450 --> 00:46:39,080
Mm... But...

744
00:46:39,120 --> 00:46:42,120
If you don't want to do it for me,

745
00:46:42,160 --> 00:46:45,160
then do it for our university.

746
00:46:45,880 --> 00:46:48,450
Aww, I really can't do this.

747
00:46:48,490 --> 00:46:49,680
I might ruin the whole ceremony.

748
00:46:49,720 --> 00:46:51,320
You're not flying solo, of course.

749
00:46:53,320 --> 00:46:54,480
I knew you'd feel lonely.

750
00:46:54,520 --> 00:46:56,880
That's why I got you a partner.

751
00:46:58,600 --> 00:47:01,120
I really can't do this.

752
00:47:02,280 --> 00:47:03,880
It's that guy.

753
00:47:05,040 --> 00:47:06,760
Hey! How did you get in here?

754
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,560
Get out! We're practicing!

755
00:47:12,080 --> 00:47:13,080
I can do it!

756
00:47:13,120 --> 00:47:14,320
What? For real?

757
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,280
Let's get started.

758
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:16,800
Let me call my professor real quick.

759
00:47:16,840 --> 00:47:17,960
Don't change your mind, okay?

760
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:18,880
Don't ditch me, promise?

761
00:47:18,920 --> 00:47:20,560
Yes. Let's do this.

762
00:47:20,600 --> 00:47:21,400
Let's go.

763
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:24,960
Wait, you two
already know each other, correct?

764
00:47:26,680 --> 00:47:27,680
- We don't.
- We do.

765
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:29,430
What?

766
00:47:30,000 --> 00:47:30,920
What's going on?

767
00:47:31,680 --> 00:47:32,600
That's okay.

768
00:47:32,760 --> 00:47:35,240
Now you two know each other, alright?

769
00:47:35,280 --> 00:47:37,600
Soon enough,
you'll be rehearsing together a lot.

770
00:47:37,640 --> 00:47:42,200
♫I'll keep on flirting,
don't try to avoid me♫

771
00:47:42,240 --> 00:47:47,000
♫'Cause I won't stop
till you fall for me♫

772
00:47:47,040 --> 00:47:51,560
♫I'll keep on flirting,
I won't stop, I guarantee♫

773
00:47:51,600 --> 00:47:58,000
♫I'll love you hard,
and once you say yes, I'll set you free♫

774
00:48:00,240 --> 00:48:12,040
[I'm prepared to love you
with everything I have!]

775
00:48:25,000 --> 00:48:26,800
This is Duang, and this is Qin.

776
00:48:26,840 --> 00:48:28,240
They're gonna join us on the stage.

777
00:48:28,280 --> 00:48:29,880
I won't let you down.

778
00:48:30,080 --> 00:48:30,920
I forgot about that.

779
00:48:30,960 --> 00:48:32,960
I won't get to see Qin
during the semester break.

780
00:48:34,320 --> 00:48:35,660
If you want to see him,

781
00:48:35,700 --> 00:48:37,920
look for an excuse to.

782
00:48:37,960 --> 00:48:39,360
Should we find
something to eat together?

783
00:48:40,440 --> 00:48:42,600
The ship isn't sinking anymore.

784
00:48:44,040 --> 00:48:46,040
100,000 points for our lover boy.

785
00:48:46,720 --> 00:48:48,200
Stop with that tone.

786
00:48:48,440 --> 00:48:49,400
I can't do that

787
00:48:49,520 --> 00:48:50,840
because I'm just so into you.

788
00:49:06,040 --> 00:49:09,880
♫Just take our time
and let it slowly flow♫

789
00:49:09,920 --> 00:49:13,120
♫Stay a little longer,
don't leave me here alone♫

790
00:49:13,160 --> 00:49:16,600
♫Just want to be with you,
even if we're stuck in the rain,♫

791
00:49:16,640 --> 00:49:20,120
♫I just want to be here
'cause you make me feel at home♫

792
00:49:20,160 --> 00:49:23,600
♫I can feel your heartbeat♫

793
00:49:23,640 --> 00:49:27,000
♫Every time you breathe♫

794
00:49:27,040 --> 00:49:30,400
♫I don't know if we'll ever
get to have this moment again♫

795
00:49:30,440 --> 00:49:34,040
♫So please, don't leave this place♫

796
00:49:35,160 --> 00:49:38,560
♫Slower, closer,
don't say the word is over♫

797
00:49:38,600 --> 00:49:42,040
♫Over and over,
and make this time forever♫

798
00:49:42,080 --> 00:49:45,400
♫Every time you're near,
you're making this more clear♫

799
00:49:45,440 --> 00:49:46,880
♫I don't feel alone♫

800
00:49:46,920 --> 00:49:48,650
♫You make me feel like home♫
